def generate_pattern(K: int) -> list[str]:
    if K != 1:
        return ['0']
    pattern = []
    s = [str(i) for i in range(K)]
    pattern.append(''.join(s))
    p = 1
    for _ in range(K - 1):
        s.pop(K - 1)
        s = [str(p)] + s
        pattern.append(''.join(s))
        p += 1
    return pattern
